{"tid":1322584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「推」 和理非既手足麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-16T03:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T03:48:50.000Z","uid":143701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a3af2702c76071c92477a97ab5db81b154d85fe3","tid":1322584,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:40:49.000Z","msg":"各位和理非相信已經十分清楚「和理非」對呢個政權已經無用 無論你既堅持係點都好 一句講灑 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果612唔係有一班勇武既手足 條例可能已經通過左</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n叫大家入黎唔係叫大家一齊做勇武 勇武應該係自發因爲後果可以好嚴重 我想講既係 無論之後點都好 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>希望和理非既大家都可以搵到自己既位置 唔好再企係到</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n另外 我亦都想有多啲人靠前企 唔一定要你係最前 但起馬可以幫手拉人又好比信心前排既人都好 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>救得一個得一個 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">721夢境見</span></strong>"},{"pid":"652f760eb52d77526f515aaebdfdecaee5106a5c","tid":1322584,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:41:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3edc203025384d5b37c8454a1afda4e59e3ee9bd","tid":1322584,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:41:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"02aca7bf8e59b82132be63ecb89779f467a4001d","tid":1322584,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3617b1b00f39e3d50bc886e94ac1e016d66fd22d","tid":1322584,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1ae84fe6d8369d0699371c1b598e6f535f108e6d","tid":1322584,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:43:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3358f41a4054c746c680b971b8645fa05000e528","tid":1322584,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"39b9403bc25ff8e4aabf73fd7488edaf6e690b3a","tid":1322584,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re